{"tid":253840,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好唔鍾意阿媽煲湯","createTime":"2017-05-22T17:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T10:14:49.000Z","uid":30821,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e898ae7ec867ddb41ff7b81f46afefecfcc1ecd","tid":253840,"uid":30821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:06:54.000Z","msg":"用花膠煲湯既人係咪戇卵鳩架？<br />\n舊野臭腥到要加花旗參黎去陣腥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住仲要加隻雞去，煲幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到煲野得返油、蛋白質同脂肪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />味道仲要係苦既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話有骨膠原。。呢d野都仲有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同佢解釋又唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd野唔係貴就有營養有益架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一聽到有煲湯就唔想返屋企食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n烏啄啄兮烏啄啄,莫奈何兮莫奈何,你阿媽兮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9f7e755bc04ec974889161b14a3d67933d850c","tid":253840,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"不孝子"},{"pid":"aa88a07581c6751feb96ce7d43edcebecf1dbbcb","tid":253840,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:09:27.000Z","msg":"有湯飲咪算好  早排有位巴打開post講自己夜晚果餐食半斤菜心咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bb2c634898cc9f98168f02af8a2d63b8e2362f","tid":253840,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不孝子</blockquote><br />\n愚孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f1941fd4aa93d433cc76c3ef276539bafe4f43","tid":253840,"uid":112772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:10:51.000Z","msg":"阿媽煲湯比你你就唔好嫌三嫌四啦"},{"pid":"1b0b55d4477428c2d68c5687f10cc5a77778681f","tid":253840,"uid":43594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:11:32.000Z","msg":"咁係你呀媽唔識煲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011b324b676fc37fc8ec2a2128291e743208b64d","tid":253840,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有湯飲咪算好  早排有位巴打開post講自己夜晚果餐食半斤菜心咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己煎隻蛋加d豉油囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d212aaab77068212b8638ab495bef508a47cff3","tid":253840,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:13:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"509fbe221a5ee14dba35d87143605b0d721c94fb","tid":253840,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老母以前煲湯都幾好飲<br />\n<br />\n而家成日聽埋佢d傻閪師奶朋友教路落撚埋d古靈精怪野 勁撚難飲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正是如此矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日煲藥當湯飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7960fe73d425023dd60b6c3c4870c2143def3f","tid":253840,"uid":45821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老母以前煲湯都幾好飲<br />\n<br />\n而家成日聽埋佢d傻閪師奶朋友教路落撚埋d古靈精怪野 勁撚難飲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我阿媽又係  睇埋垃圾肥媽用榴槤殼煲湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"